  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1082">
<l>nōkkiṉā ṇōkketir nōkkuta ṟākkaṇaṅku </l>
<l>tāṉaikkoṇ ṭaṉṉa tuṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This female beauty returning my looks is like a celestial maiden coming with an army to contend against me.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
